4Geeks Academy offers a Cybersecurity Bootcamp designed to help individuals become cybersecurity specialists without prior knowledge. The program spans 16 weeks and includes three live online classes weekly, with a maximum class size of 16 participants. Students will learn essential skills in Windows, Linux, network, and server administration, as well as cloud security, penetration testing, and cyber threat intelligence analysis. The course also covers risk management through data loss prevention strategies and compliance with standards like ISO 27001 and NIST. Graduates receive an official completion certificate recognized by multiple institutions. The program is available in English and Spanish. For more information, visit https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity. stop